Psalm 121

1 I líft up my éyes to the móuntains;
from whére shall come my hélp?
2 My hélp shall cóme from the LÓRD,
who made héaven and éarth.

3 He will kéep your fóot from stúmbling.
Your guárd will never slúmber.
4 Nó, he sléeps not nor slúmbers,
Ísrael’s guárd.

5 The LORD your guárd, the LÓRD your sháde
at yóur right hánd.
6 By dáy the sún shall not smíte you,
nor the móon in the níght.

7 The LÓRD will guárd you from évil;
he will guárd your sóul.
8 The LORD will guárd your góing and cóming,
both nów and foréver.
